---
// src/pages/faq.astro
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ) - WinBet"
  description="Find answers to frequently asked questions about WinBet, including account registration, deposits, withdrawals, and how to play slot games."
>
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-[#ffd700]">
      Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)
    </h1>
    <div class="space-y-6 text-lg">
      <p>
        Welcome to the FAQ section of WinBet. Here, you'll find answers to the
        most common questions about how to use our platform, play our slot
        games, make deposits and withdrawals, and more. If you have any
        additional questions, feel free to contact our support team.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        1. How do I create an account on WinBet?
      </h2>
      <p>Creating an account is simple. Just follow these steps:</p>
      <ol class="list-decimal pl-6">
        <li>Click the "Sign Up" button located at the top of the page.</li>
        <li>
          Fill in the required information, including your name, email, and a
          secure password.
        </li>
        <li>
          Complete the KYC (Know Your Customer) process to verify your identity.
        </li>
        <li>
          Once registered, you can log in to your account using your
          credentials.
        </li>
      </ol>
      <p>
        After registration, make sure to check your email inbox for a
        confirmation link.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        2. How do I log in to my WinBet account?
      </h2>
      <p>To log in to your account:</p>
      <ol class="list-decimal pl-6">
        <li>Click the "Log In" button at the top of the page.</li>
        <li>Enter your email and password.</li>
        <li>
          If you’ve forgotten your password, click on the "Forgot Password?"
          link to reset it.
        </li>
      </ol>
      <p>
        Once logged in, you can start playing slots or make deposits and
        withdrawals.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        3. How do I make a deposit?
      </h2>
      <p>To deposit funds into your WinBet account:</p>
      <ol class="list-decimal pl-6">
        <li>Log in to your account.</li>
        <li>
          Go to the "Banking" section and select your preferred deposit method
          (e.g., cryptocurrency, bank transfer, or mobile payment).
        </li>
        <li>Follow the instructions to complete the deposit.</li>
      </ol>
      <p>
        Deposits are usually processed instantly, except for bank transfers
        which may take up to 24 hours.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        4. How do I play slot games?
      </h2>
      <p>Playing slots on WinBet is easy:</p>
      <ol class="list-decimal pl-6">
        <li>Log in to your account.</li>
        <li>Navigate to the "Slots" section from the main menu.</li>
        <li>Select a slot game by clicking on the game icon.</li>
        <li>
          Set your bet amount and press the "Spin" button to start playing.
        </li>
      </ol>
      <p>
        Your goal is to match symbols on the reels to win. The payout varies
        depending on the game and the symbols you land.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        5. What is the minimum amount required to make a withdrawal?
      </h2>
      <p>
        The minimum withdrawal amount at WinBet is typically <strong>$20</strong
        > (or equivalent in your chosen currency or cryptocurrency). However, the
        specific amount may vary based on the payment method used.
      </p>
      <p>
        Please ensure that you have met the wagering requirements (if any)
        before attempting to withdraw.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        6. How do I make a withdrawal?
      </h2>
      <p>To withdraw your winnings:</p>
      <ol class="list-decimal pl-6">
        <li>Log in to your account.</li>
        <li>Go to the "Banking" section and select the withdrawal method.</li>
        <li>
          Enter the amount you wish to withdraw and follow the on-screen
          instructions.
        </li>
      </ol>
      <p>
        Withdrawals are typically processed within 1-3 business days, depending
        on the method used.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        7. Are there any fees for deposits or withdrawals?
      </h2>
      <p>
        At WinBet, we strive to keep your banking experience as cost-effective
        as possible. Generally, we do not charge any fees for deposits or
        withdrawals. However, some payment providers or cryptocurrency networks
        may charge a small transaction fee.
      </p>
      <p>
        Any fees associated with your payment method will be clearly displayed
        during the deposit or withdrawal process.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        8. What should I do if I encounter issues with deposits, withdrawals, or
        games?
      </h2>
      <p>
        If you experience any issues, please contact our customer support team
        for assistance. You can reach us via:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
        <li>Live Chat (available 24/7)</li>
        <li>
          Email: <a
            href="mailto:support@winbet.com"
            class="text-[#ffd700] underline">support@winbet.com</a
          >
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Our support team will help resolve any issues you may encounter quickly
        and efficiently.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        9. Can I play WinBet's slots on mobile devices?
      </h2>
      <p>
        Yes! WinBet's slots are fully optimized for mobile play. You can access
        the games directly from your smartphone or tablet’s web browser. There
        is no need to download any apps—simply log in and play.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        10. Is WinBet available in my country?
      </h2>
      <p>
        WinBet is available to players in many countries, but there may be some
        restrictions depending on your jurisdiction. Please refer to our terms
        and conditions or contact our support team for more information about
        the availability of WinBet in your region.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
